https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965","stars":5123,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":39,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":563890,"username":"Mateverse","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Mateverse","website":"","twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":"","tagline":"","bio":".replace(\"meta\",\"mate\")\r\n阴阳怪气直接B","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6525/538c/563890_mini.png?m=1658798896","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6525/538c/563890_normal.png?m=1658798896","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6525/538c/563890_large.png?m=1658798896","avatar_xlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6525/538c/563890_xlarge.png?m=1658798896","avatar_xxlarge":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6525/538c/563890_xlarge.png?m=1658798896","created":1638343584,"last_modified":1658798896},"last_reply_by":"Cassius","last_touched":1660616472,"title":"Android13 正式版发布","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/873099","created":1660612549,"deleted":0,"content":"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2022/08/android-13-is-in-aosp.html\r\n\r\n省流手动总结：\r\n\r\n1. Material You 动态颜色扩展到所有应用图标\r\n2. 针对 APP 的多语言设置\r\n3. 文本的字体优化\r\n4. 矢量的 emoji/表情字符\r\n5. 无需到状态栏设置，可以在 APP 内提示添加快速设置磁贴（ Quick Settings Placement API ）\r\n6. 可编程的着色器，需要注意的是，Android12 就提供了 blur 特效，可以电这里查看： https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/graphics/agsl\r\n7. 媒体播放控制栏添加了更多的操作选项，例如添加的 XX 播放列表，或者转移当前媒体到 XX 设备播放\r\n8. BLE 音频支持\r\n9. MIDI 2.0\r\n10. Android 13 核心库现在与 OpenJDK 11 LTS 版本保持一致\r\n11. 针对平板进行了优化\r\n12. 可以针对 APP 设置允许访问照片范围\r\n13. 运行时通知权限的优化 （这个我没懂，可以看这里的说明 https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/ui/notifiers/notification-permission ）\r\n14. 可以无需拿到定位，读取附近 WIFI 的权限\r\n15. 媒体文件访问的精细权限。不仅针对照片，对其他媒体以及文件也可以单独设置访问权限\r\n16. 从 Android 13 开始，应用可以撤消先前由系统或用户授予的运行时权限。\r\n17. 更安全的导出 Intent 过滤器","content_rendered":"<p><a href=\"https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2022/08/android-13-is-in-aosp.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://android-developers.googleblog.com/2022/08/android-13-is-in-aosp.html</a></p>\n<p>省流手动总结：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Material You 动态颜色扩展到所有应用图标</li>\n<li>针对 APP 的多语言设置</li>\n<li>文本的字体优化</li>\n<li>矢量的 emoji/表情字符</li>\n<li>无需到状态栏设置，可以在 APP 内提示添加快速设置磁贴（ Quick Settings Placement API ）</li>\n<li>可编程的着色器，需要注意的是，Android12 就提供了 blur 特效，可以电这里查看： <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/graphics/agsl\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/graphics/agsl</a></li>\n<li>媒体播放控制栏添加了更多的操作选项，例如添加的 XX 播放列表，或者转移当前媒体到 XX 设备播放</li>\n<li>BLE 音频支持</li>\n<li>MIDI 2.0</li>\n<li>Android 13 核心库现在与 OpenJDK 11 LTS 版本保持一致</li>\n<li>针对平板进行了优化</li>\n<li>可以针对 APP 设置允许访问照片范围</li>\n<li>运行时通知权限的优化 （这个我没懂，可以看这里的说明 <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/ui/notifiers/notification-permission\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://developer.android.com/guide/topics/ui/notifiers/notification-permission</a> ）</li>\n<li>可以无需拿到定位，读取附近 WIFI 的权限</li>\n<li>媒体文件访问的精细权限。不仅针对照片，对其他媒体以及文件也可以单独设置访问权限</li>\n<li>从 Android 13 开始，应用可以撤消先前由系统或用户授予的运行时权限。</li>\n<li>更安全的导出 Intent 过滤器</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1660612549,"replies":19,"id":873099},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":188733,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","stars":3535,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":559928,"username":"OkabeRintaro","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/OkabeRintaro","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a96e/f66b/559928_mini.png?m=1651838433","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a96e/f66b/559928_normal.png?m=1651838433","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a96e/f66b/55